   25. You have been hired to design the memory system for Big Eyes Bertha, 
   a doll that takes pictures throught its eyes. If Big Eyes Bertha uses 18 
   bits per pixel (6 for Red, 6 for Green, and 6 for Blue) in an RGB system,
   how much memory will it need to store one 200 x 300 pixel image?